OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLabour pledges to replace  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnon-dom tax status         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Labour has pledged to replace the      
OL,6, so-called "non-dom" taxpayer status in 
OL,7, the UK after a row over the finances of
OL,8, Chancellor Rishi Sunak's wife.         
OL,10,FThe party said the status was unfair.  
OL,11,FIt allows UK residents whose permanent 
OL,12,Fhomes are abroad not to pay UK tax on  
OL,13,Foverseas income.                       
OL,15,FInstead, it would introduce a          
OL,16,Fshorter-term scheme for those staying  
OL,17,Fin the UK for up to five years.        
OL,19,FShadow chancellor Rachel Reeves said it
OL,20,Fwould end "outdated tax perks".        
